narration_text: #C C puts hands on her waist.
#C C picks a bottle from cabinet.
#C C puts bottle on the table.
#C C picks a plastic can from the fridge.
#C C puts the can in the fridge.
#C C picks up a cup from shelf.
#C C places a cup on the sink.
#C C pours water in the cup with the kettle.
#C C picks a plate from the shelf.
#C C puts plate on the table.
#C C picks up a cooking spoon.
#C C serves #unsure in a plate with the cooking spoon.
#C C dries hands using hand towel.
